    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it's a total dream. This car is in truly stunning condition\u2014practically flawless and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered, garage-kept, and loved every single day. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. I'd love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
